      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants a project, a parts car, or just a cheap runabout. It has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect at this level, but there\u2019s still value here for the right buyer. If you\u2019re handy or just want something inexpensive to work with, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
