      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Tough old runner with strong project, work-truck, or budget commuter potential. Advertised in poor condition, but it still offers a solid mechanical starting point with usable power delivery, dependable drivetrain feel, and the kind of straightforward platform enthusiasts like because it\u2019s easy to sort and improve. Cosmetically rough and showing its age, yet it has the kind of honest wear that makes it a practical buy for someone who values utility over appearance. Great candidate for a fixer-upper, parts donor, or inexpensive get-around vehicle.",
